V0154_01_00_00_0.text: If you're my opponent, this should be one incredible Duel!

V0154_01_00_01_0.text: If it's a fight you want, count me in!

V0154_01_00_02_0.text:
Howdy, mate!
I'd love to Duel ya!

V0154_01_00_03_0.text:
Whoa, girl.
What's got you all a tether?

V0154_01_00_03_1.text: How about I Duel for ya?

V0154_01_00_04_0.text:
Jaden!
Let's have a great Duel, mate!

V0154_01_00_05_0.text:
I’d love a fair go!
Dinos are some of my favorite creatures!

V0154_01_00_06_0.text:
Sure - I'll Duel ya!
After all, you and Shirley are cousins!

V0154_01_00_07_0.text:
I gotta be careful.
Alexis has more bite than Shirley!

V0154_01_00_08_0.text: I know you're trapped in there, but I’ll set you free!

V0154_01_00_09_0.text:
Don't give in!
Darkness hasn't taken you yet!

V0154_01_00_10_0.text: I have to defeat Jaden's dark half - the Supreme King!

V0154_03_00_00_0.text: If you wanna battle to the end, I'm happy to oblige!

V0154_03_00_01_0.text: It's time to put this Duel to bed!

V0154_03_00_03_0.text:
I know, Shirley.
I've got this!

V0154_03_00_04_0.text:
That was a great combo!
But I got an even greater one!

V0154_05_00_00_0.text: When the bandage falls, my Eye of Orichalcum sees the truth!

V0154_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0154_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0154_16_00_00_0.text: This will be the last battle!

V0154_21_00_04_0.text: You can knock me down, but I can get back up!

V0154_28_00_00_0.text:
Sorry!
Went a bit overboard there!

V0154_28_00_01_0.text:
Phew!
Good thing I didn't underestimate ya!

V0154_28_00_02_0.text:
Nice Duel, mate!
One for the ages!

V0154_28_00_03_0.text:
No need to throw a wobbly.
This was a friendly game!

V0154_28_00_04_0.text:
Great Duel, Hassleberry!
I'm proud to have faced ya!

V0154_28_00_06_0.text:
C'mon, Jaden!
You're stronger than the dark!

V0154_29_00_00_0.text:
What a Duel!
You got me tuckered out!

V0154_29_00_01_0.text:
That was a ripper! 
Good on ya!

V0154_29_00_02_0.text:
Sorry, Shirley!
Things went a bit crook during the Duel.

V0154_29_00_03_0.text:
Congratulations!
I didn't stand a chance!

V0154_29_00_04_0.text: The Supreme King is in complete control of Jaden's soul...

V0154_29_00_05_0.text: The shadows in Jaden's heart are stronger than I imagined!

V0154_33_00_00_0.text:
The Eye of Orichalcum!
Show me what you see!

V0154_30_00_00_0.text:
Down, girl! Heel!
Let 'em go, Shirley!

V0154_30_00_01_0.text: You still have the heart of a Duelist!

V0154_30_00_02_0.text: Don't get so hot under the collar!

V0154_34_00_04_0.text: Get out! I don't need ya!

V0154_34_00_06_0.text: My right eye speaks to me...

V0154_34_00_07_0.text: Which way is the comet's tail turnin?

V0154_34_00_08_0.text: My Eye of Orichalcum will help me save my friends.

V0154_34_00_09_0.text: My cards are asking me to dig 'em up!

V0154_34_00_10_0.text: You never need a reason to make a new friend!

V0154_35_00_00_0.text:
The name's Jim Cook!
Master of archeological Dueling!

V0154_36_00_02_0.text: Sorry. Things went a bit wonky.

V0154_36_00_03_0.text: I leave the rest to you, mate!

V0154_08_00_00_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Fossil Fusion!

V0154_08_00_00_1.text: I'll dig bones out of the earth and fuse 'em together!

V0154_08_00_01_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Fossil Fusion!

V0154_08_00_01_1.text: I dig up my monster and yours and combine 'em together!

V0154_08_00_02_0.text: I activate Fossil Fusion's effect from my Graveyard!

V0154_08_00_02_1.text: When a Fossil Fusion Monster's destroyed, I get this back!

V0154_08_00_03_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Time Stream!

V0154_08_00_03_1.text: It rewinds time to devolve this monster!

V0154_08_00_04_0.text: I activate Time Stream's effect from my Graveyard!

V0154_08_00_04_1.text: I banish these cards to revive a Fossil Fusion Monster!

V0154_08_00_05_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Miracle Rupture!

V0154_08_00_05_1.text: I bury a Level 4 or lower Rock monster from my deck!

V0154_08_00_06_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Specimen Inspection!

V0154_08_00_06_1.text: It buries a monster that has the Type and Level I choose!

V0154_08_00_07_0.text:
I activate my Trap Card!
Sakuretsu Armor!

V0154_08_00_08_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Release from Stone!

V0154_08_00_08_1.text: It Special Summons a banished Rock monster!

V0154_09_00_00_1.text: I discard a card to revive your monster to my field!

V0154_09_00_01_0.text: When Skull Convoy destroys your monster, you take damage!

V0154_09_00_02_1.text: It swaps your monster's ATK and DEF during this battle!

V0154_09_00_03_0.text: Skull Buggy's effect activates when it destroys a monster!

V0154_09_00_04_0.text: I activate Skull Buggy's effect from my Graveyard!

V0154_09_00_04_1.text: I banish it to add a monster with Fossil Fusion in its text!

V0154_09_00_05_0.text: Skull Bone's effect activates from the Graveyard!

V0154_09_00_05_1.text: I banish it to acquire Time Stream from my deck!

V0154_09_00_06_0.text: Skullgar's effect activates from the Graveyard!

V0154_09_00_06_1.text: I banish it to get Fossil Fusion from my deck!

V0154_09_00_07_0.text: Skull Wagon's effect activates when it destroys a monster!

V0154_09_00_08_0.text: I banish Skull Wagon from my Graveyard to use its effect!

V0154_09_00_08_1.text: It destroys one Spell or Trap Card on the field!

V0154_09_00_09_0.text: When Skull Knight destroys a monster, it can attack again!

V0154_09_00_10_0.text: I banish Skull Knight from the Graveyard to use its effect!

V0154_09_00_10_1.text: It destroys one monster on the field!

V0154_09_00_11_0.text: Shell Knight's effect activates when it's summoned!

V0154_09_00_13_1.text: All Special Summoned monsters on the field are destroyed!

V0154_09_00_14_0.text: Flint Cragger's effect activates when it's Special Summoned!

V0154_09_00_15_0.text: Flint Cragger's effect will knock some sense into ya!

V0154_09_00_15_1.text: By sendin this card to the Graveyard, you take damage!

V0154_09_00_17_0.text:
Argh!
Weathering Soldier loses ATK every End Phase!

V0154_09_00_18_0.text: When Fossil Tusker destroys a monster, its effect activates!

V0154_09_00_19_0.text: Tribute Summoning The Tyrant Neptune activates its effect!

V0154_09_00_19_1.text: It gains the name and effects of the monster I Tributed!

V0154_09_00_20_1.text: I can Special Summon up to three Reptile and Rock monsters!

V0154_09_00_21_0.text: Spawn Alligator's effect activates during the End Phase!

V0154_09_00_21_1.text: It revives one of the monsters used to Tribute Summon it!

V0154_09_00_22_0.text: Tribute Summoning Dark Alligator activates its effect!

V0154_13_00_00_0.text: I bring out Fossil Warrior Skull King!

V0154_13_00_01_0.text:
This beaut has plenty a' drive!
Fossil Machine Skull Convoy!

V0154_13_00_02_0.text: Here's the one and only Fossil Dragon Skullgios!

V0154_13_00_04_0.text:
Come on out!
Fossil Warrior Skull Bone!

V0154_13_00_05_0.text: Rising from the depths of the earth!

V0154_13_00_06_0.text:
Come here!
Fossil Machine Skull Wagon!

V0154_13_00_07_0.text:
Let's go!
Fossil Warrior Skull Knight!

V0154_13_00_19_0.text: I Special Summon an Alligator Token!

V0154_19_00_01_1.text: Pop it into first and attack!

V0154_19_00_09_0.text: Gaia Plate cuts your monster's ATK and DEF in half!
